moduleMetadataJson.name: Search Engine Domain Email Address Collector
moduleMetadataJson.description:
This module uses Google, Bing and Yahoo to create a list of
        valid email addresses for the target domain.
author: Carlos Perez <carlos_perez@darkoperator.com>

options.name: WORKSPACE
options.description: Specify the workspace for this module

options.name: DOMAIN
options.description: The domain name to locate email addresses for

options.name: SEARCH_GOOGLE
options.description: Enable Google as a backend search engine

options.name: SEARCH_BING
options.description: Enable Bing as a backend search engine

options.name: SEARCH_YAHOO
options.description: Enable Yahoo! as a backend search engine

options.name: OUTFILE
options.description: A filename to store the generated email list
